title: 279 #403 one of a kind!
posting_body: ['The Syper Group welcomes you to 279 Kosciuszko located in the heart of Bed-Stuy.', 'These apartments exude all that is expected in a modern apartment from the colors in the hallway to the carefully thought out architecture of the apartments.', 'Top of the line appliances and features make this a one-of-a-kind place to call home.', 'Exceptional closet space can be boasted as well as a spa-worthy shower will have you running, not walking, to go home to.', 'While at home, enjoy the in-house laundry to maximize your time and get into the city via G, J, or M trains which are a quick walking distance away.', 'In the area you can find supermarkets, restaurants, bars and home goods stores available for your shopping convenience.', 'Stay home and enjoy your state-of-the-art apartment.', 'Fee due at signing', 'video available upon request', 'Please Text Perets at 312-881-9553 for flexible showings.']
